(23, 'content', 0, '"<p>These are courses suitable for teachers of instrumental music who would like to obtain formal credentials and a stronger foundation in music education:<\\/p>\\r\\n<h1>PIANO PEDAGOGY<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p><strong>KPP100:<\\/strong> Certificate in Piano Pedagogy<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>KPP200:<\\/strong> Higher Certificate in Piano Pedagogy<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>KPP300:<\\/strong> Diploma in Piano Pedagogy<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h1>BOWED STRINGS PEDAGOGY<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p><strong>BST100:<\\/strong> Certificate in the Teaching of Bowed String Instruments<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>BST200:<\\/strong> Higher Certificate in the Teaching of Bowed String Instruments<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>BST300:<\\/strong> Diploma in the Teaching of Bowed String Instruments<\\/p>"', '', '2013-03-07 12:00:00', '2013-03-07 12:00:00', '', NULL),
